<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9596</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15264</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天早上，孩子们吃早饭的速度特别快。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15265</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21076</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一想到能再次见到休伊，大家都很兴奋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21077</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25154</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哪儿着火了？”玛莎阿姨问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25155</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29381</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊给大家使了个眼色。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29382</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35249</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们都保证过不会向任何人提起休伊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35250</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41293</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们今天只是去树林里转转。”鲍比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41294</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44244</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的嘴里塞满了煎饼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44245</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51392</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>前一天，赛伊按照休伊的要求将它送回了井底。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51393</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57987</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比非常聪明，他在通往那口井的小路上做了标记。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57988</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65306</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但他们找那条小路找了很久，却还是在原地打转。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65307</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71664</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你确定是这条路吗，鲍比？”简嘀咕道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71665</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76032</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你用什么做标记的？”潘瑟问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76033</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79562</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“花生啊。”鲍比回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79563</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89133</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>遗憾的是，鲍比用来在小路上做标记的那些花生都被浣熊一家子吃光了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89134</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96992</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很好！我们永远也找不到小路了！”赛伊大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96993</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101136</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们迷茫地看看四周。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101137</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105642</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“走这条路试试吧！”潘瑟说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105643</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109313</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们向她说的方向走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109314</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117123</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>几个小时过去了，但他们依然连那口井的影子都没看到。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117124</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126039</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们迷路了。我们现在永远都不会找到休伊了。”简抱怨说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126040</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128719</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“等等！那边是什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128720</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134667</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊指着某个地方，他激动地跳了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134668</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138096</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看！我们找到那口井了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138097</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141312</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们跑向了那口井。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141313</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149649</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊迅速将木桶放到了井底并把那个贝壳拉了上来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149650</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156681</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“休伊！休伊！” 他们一起叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156682</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162309</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>休伊慢慢从他的壳里探出了脑袋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162310</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167589</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，又是你们！”他迷迷糊糊地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167590</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174061</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我还在希望遇见你们不过是个糟糕的梦而已。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174062</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183250</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟决定友好地问一些事情：“休伊，你怎么会在这个井里呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183251</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188993</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这对你们来说可能就是一口老井，”休伊说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188994</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195309</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但这口井对我们这样的海洋生物来说却是一个旅行站。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195310</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199259</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你要去哪里？”简问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199260</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203588</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要去马维斯提见我的兄弟们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203588</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207929</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这口井不过是个临时停留的地方。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207929</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217348</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你的意思是，你要离开？”鲍比哀叹道，“什么时候？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217250</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222424</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“时间到了的时候。”休伊肯定地回答，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222425</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225983</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在，你们想好了愿望没有？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225984</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233825</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所有孩子都非常激动，但却都没想好要许什么样的愿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233865</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237778</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们互相看看对方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237779</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244264</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我可没时间一天到晚的这样等着，你们也一样。”休伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244265</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249924</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我觉得赛伊应该第一个许愿。”简说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249925</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255340</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢你，简。”赛伊沾沾自喜地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255341</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261120</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“为什么是赛伊第一个？”鲍比抱怨说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261121</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>267319</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们三个人争论的时候，潘瑟小声跟自己说：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>267319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270958</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我希望我们都美丽英俊。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270958</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>277112</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，休伊的鳍发出了粉红和红色的光芒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>277064</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280843</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它们优雅地开合了三次。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280844</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>286969</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们停止了争论，全都惊奇地看着休伊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>286970</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>292921</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后他们看到一团白雾。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>292922</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>297655</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“发生了什么？”鲍比害怕地问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>297656</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>302423</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你的愿望正在实现。”休伊回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>302424</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>308770</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们的愿望？什么愿望？”赛伊疑惑地问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>308771</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>313574</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们感觉那些雾离开了自己的脸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>313575</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>318259</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“变得美丽英俊的愿望啊。”休伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>318260</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>325130</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊、鲍比和简互相看着，又看看潘瑟。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>325131</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>330056</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们都在想休伊说的是什么意思，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>330057</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>335671</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但孩子们在盯着对方的时候互相都不认识了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>335672</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>338782</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就像潘瑟许的愿一样，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>338783</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>346331</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们每个人都变得像电影明星一样美丽英俊了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>